posting_body: ['Address:  14780 Fluorine St NW,  Ramsey  MN   55303', 'Description:  This property is professionally managed.', ' Beautiful 3 Bedroom Home For Rent ~ Ramsey, MN:', 'The main level features; Large living room, kitchen with granite counter tops, new appliances and cupboards, informal dining area exiting to a large tiered deck, two bedrooms and a bathroom.', 'Lower level includes; family room with fireplace, bedroom with a walk through bathroom featuring a jetted tub, and the laundry room.', "You'll find several upgrades/updates to this home including flooring, neutral decor, carpet and paint.", 'Home is located on a quiet cul-de-sac and has a beautiful backyard.', 'A full appliance package including washer and dryer.', 'NO PETS ALLOWED!!', ' This is a NO smoking property.', ' This is NOT Section 8 approved.', 'Information:', 'Rent Rate:  $ 1,995', 'Security Deposit:  $ 1,995', 'Available:  10/01/2022', 'Sq Ft (approx):  1,940', 'Parking:  3 car attached', 'Lease Terms:  Minimum 12 month lease.', ' Full background and credit check required on all tenants over 18 years.', 'If you are interested in viewing this property, please visit our website at <URL> and complete the Tenant Questionnaire.', ' Upon receipt, a leasing agent will be in touch to set up a showing.', ' Please be as complete as possible in order to avoid showing delays!', 'Property listed by Acuity Group / 564 Dodge Ave, Suite A / Elk River.']
